Happy Holidays, ugli3s! New episodes of The Boulet Brothers’ Dragula will resume on January 8. Enjoy the break, and be sure to binge the entire Dragula collection all holiday long on Shudder and AMC+ including Titans, Resurrection, and Seasons 1-5 of the main series.

Thanks to everyone for joining us on a dark ride from hell this year! We are eternally grateful for your undying support, and promise even more murder and mayhem in 2024. Highlights: winning a MUAH award for best makeup, touring the US & Australia with the Titans cast, writing and directing “The Boulet Brothers Halfway to Halloween TV Special” and “The Boulet Brothers’ Dragula” S5, doing a bit of hosting for AMC’s Fear Fest, headlining Midsummer Scream, and ringing in Halloween on Good Morning America! Happy New Year to you all, and we wish you love, happiness, wealth and success in 2024. 🦇🦇
